    "Additional 5% instances are incrementally added.",
    "As shown in Figure 11a (Anthropic-Helpful) and Figure 11b (Anthropic-HH), applying self-curation quickly reaches peak performance in the early stage, while the baseline improves slowly and plateaus at a lower level.",
